overview: Dane Granger is a 25 year old lesbian from a small town in Indiana who has always dreamed big. She reaches for the stars and happened to fall hard for the hometown sweetheart Grace Harper. Grace has demons. Dane has demons. And their demons are hellbent on destroying each other. Dane slips into madness and heartbreak in this self discovery story. Falling in love can be the most painful experience in life.
tagline: Madness is the symptom, love is the disease
title: Dane Granger
